<rdf:Description
    rdf:about="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/901"
    trackback:ping="http://www.notapathetic.com/cgi-bin/trackback.cgi/901"
    dc:title="I am not voting because, like 93% of..."
    dc:identifier="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/901"
    dc:description="I am not voting because, like 93% of this population, I am not religious, and as such I am now a second class citizen in this country.  

